(247, 'default', 'Post updated', 'App\\Models\\CMS\\Post', NULL, 21, 'App\\Models\\User', 1, '{\"changes\": {\"title\": \"MEMA 2026 — The Gospel Music Awards Gala is Coming to Nairobi!\", \"content\": \"<p>We are excited to announce the upcoming <strong>Myogenic Excellence Music Awards (MEMA) 2026 Gala</strong> — a landmark celebration of gospel music talent across Kenya and Africa.</p><p>MEMA 2026 is set to take place on <strong>September 16, 2026 in Kisumu, Kenya</strong>, bringing together the finest gospel artists, producers, videographers, and photographers for a night of recognition, music, and excellence.</p><h2>What is MEMA?</h2><p>The Myogenic Excellence Music Awards (MEMA) is a premier platform dedicated to honouring Africa\'s gospel music voices and sounds. From the emerging artist finding their footing to the seasoned producer shaping the industry — MEMA celebrates it all.</p><h2>Award Categories</h2><ul><li>Female Artist of the Year</li><li>Male Artist of the Year</li><li>Emerging Gospel Artist of the Year</li><li>Gospel Song of the Year</li><li>Gospel Video of the Year</li><li>Gospel Collaboration of the Year</li><li>Audio Producer of the Year</li><li>Video Director of the Year</li><li>Photography of the Year</li></ul><h2>Key Dates</h2><ul><li><strong>Nominations Open:</strong> April 16, 2026</li><li><strong>Nominations Close:</strong> July 15, 2026</li><li><strong>Voting Opens:</strong> August 1, 2026</li><li><strong>Voting Closes:</strong> September 14, 2026</li><li><strong>MEMA Gala Night:</strong> September 16, 2026 — Kisumu, Kenya</li></ul><h2>How to Get Involved</h2><p>You can be part of this historic event in three ways:</p><ol><li><strong>Nominate</strong> — Do you know a deserving gospel artist or creative? Nominate them starting April 16 at <a href=\\\"https://tuqiohub.africa/nominate\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">tuqiohub.africa/nominate</a>.</li><li><strong>Vote</strong> — Cast your votes for your favourite nominees from August 1. Each vote costs KES 100, with bundle discounts available.</li><li><strong>Attend</strong> — Get your tickets and join us for the gala night. Early Bird tickets go on sale April 16!</li></ol><p>Stay tuned for more updates. Follow us on social media and visit <a href=\\\"https://tuqiohub.africa\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">tuqiohub.africa</a> for the latest news on MEMA 2026.</p><p><em>Honouring Africa\'s Voices and Sounds.</em></p>\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-26 12:42:44\", \"published_at\": \"2026-03-16 09:57:00\"}}', NULL, '2026-03-26 09:42:44', '2026-03-26 09:42:44'),
(248, 'default', 'Post updated', 'App\\Models\\CMS\\Post', NULL, 23, 'App\\Models\\User', 1, '{\"changes\": {\"content\": \"<p>MEMA 2026 recognises excellence across <strong>9 award categories</strong> covering every dimension of gospel music creation. Here is what each category celebrates:</p><h3>1. Female Artist of the Year</h3><p>Recognising the most impactful female gospel artist of 2026 — an artist whose music, ministry, and influence have resonated with audiences across Kenya and Africa.</p><h3>2. Male Artist of the Year</h3><p>Celebrating outstanding male gospel artistry, ministry impact, and chart performance throughout the year.</p><h3>3. Emerging Gospel Artist of the Year</h3><p>Honouring the brightest new gospel talent on the rise — an artist who broke through in 2025–2026 with fresh sound and genuine ministry.</p><h3>4. Gospel Song of the Year</h3><p>The single gospel track that moved hearts, topped church playlists, and defined the sound of the year.</p><h3>5. Gospel Video of the Year</h3><p>Outstanding visual storytelling in gospel music video production — judged on creativity, production quality, and ministry message.</p><h3>6. Gospel Collaboration of the Year</h3><p>The most memorable gospel partnership — two or more artists coming together for a release that was greater than the sum of its parts.</p><h3>7. Audio Producer of the Year</h3><p>Excellence in gospel music production and sound engineering — the producer behind the hits.</p><h3>8. Video Director of the Year</h3><p>Creative direction and visual mastery in gospel videography — directors who bring gospel songs to stunning visual life.</p><h3>9. Photography of the Year</h3><p>Capturing the soul of gospel music through powerful imagery — event photography, artist portraits, and worship moments.</p><p>Nominations for all 8 public categories are open until July 15, 2026. <a href=\\\"/nominate?event=mema-gala-2026\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Submit your nomination now →</a></p>\", \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-26 13:03:38\", \"published_at\": \"2026-03-26 12:20:00\", \"reading_time\": 2, \"featured_image\": \"posts/featured-images/AbgODRnpS9uRbXPuqbdSmJNo825sAlL4POf7lStp.webp\"}}', NULL, '2026-03-26 10:03:38', '2026-03-26 10:03:38'),
