(15, '9b744fa9-e8e6-495a-bd34-ef1f6a46bda4', 2, NULL, 9, 4, 'Event Marketing: Best Practices and Trends', 'event-marketing-best-practices-and-trends', 'The event management landscape continues to evolve with new technologies and innovative approaches. Organizations are discovering that creating memora...', '<p>The event management landscape continues to evolve with new technologies and innovative approaches. Organizations are discovering that creating memorable experiences requires a combination of strategic planning, audience engagement, and seamless execution.</p><p>In today\'s digital age, event organizers have access to powerful tools that streamline ticketing, enhance attendee experiences, and provide valuable insights through data analytics. These platforms enable organizers to focus on what matters most: creating exceptional events that resonate with their audience.</p><p>Successful events are built on strong foundations of communication, collaboration, and creativity. By leveraging modern event management solutions, organizers can reduce administrative overhead while increasing attendee satisfaction and engagement.</p><p>The future of events lies in hybrid experiences that blend physical and virtual elements, creating opportunities for broader participation and enhanced accessibility. This evolution opens new possibilities for event organizers to reach global audiences while maintaining the intimacy of in-person connections.</p>', 'posts/featured-images/rLCgD3jDHIiQyxfE48COXYIUOxkvgyxZzutkPidd.webp', 'Event Marketing: Best Practices and Trends', 'published', '2026-02-17 17:44:00', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Event Marketing: Best Practices and Trends - Tech Events Kenya', 'The event management landscape continues to evolve with new technologies and innovative approaches. Organizations are discovering that creating memora...', 'events, ticketing, voting, awards', 'media/posts/post-image-7.jpg', 'The event management landscape continues to evolve with new technologi